## Quickstart

```bash
docker compose up -d
docker compose logs -f ollama-pull
```

Mở `http://localhost`:
1. Đăng ký admin account (lần đầu).
2. Settings → Model Providers → add Ollama (endpoint `http://ollama:11434`).
3. Tạo app type "Chatflow" hoặc "Workflow" → kéo-thả node.

## Add MCP tool

```bash
perfectrag add mcp tavily --project .
docker compose restart api worker
```

Dify cũng có plugin marketplace riêng trong UI.

